{
  "texts": [
    "Task Description: An instruction (might include an Input inside it), two responses to evaluate (denoted as Response A and Response B), and an evaluation criteria are given. 1.",
    "Write a detailed feedback that assess the quality of the two responses strictly based on the given evaluation criteria, not evaluating in general. 2.",
    "Make comparisons between Response A and Response B.",
    "Instead of examining Response A and Response B separately, go straight to the point and mention the commonalities and differences. 3.",
    "After writing the feedback, indicate the better response, either \"A\" or \"B\". 4."
  ]
}